---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/mainLayouts.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Suscripción | LinkApp"
  description="¡Gracias por tu interés en suscribirte a LinkApp! Con una suscripción, podrás disfrutar de características exclusivas."
>
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 py-24 overflow-hidden">
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl w-full">
      <header class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase text-white mb-6">
          Planes y <span class="gradient-text">Precios</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-200 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-medium custom-shadow text-center">
          Escala tu organización digital con funciones diseñadas para la eficiencia y el minimalismo.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-stretch">
        <!-- Plan Comunidad -->
        <div class="group p-10 bg-[#18181b] border border-white/10 rounded-[2.5rem] hover:border-blue/50 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col shadow-2xl">
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-blue mb-2">Comunidad</h3>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 text-white">
              <span class="text-4xl font-black">FREE</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm mt-4">Perfil básico personal con acceso a funciones limitadas.</p>
          </div>
          
          <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 flex-grow">
            <li class="text-zinc-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue">✓</span> Perfil básico personal
            </li>
            <li class="text-zinc-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue">✓</span> Hasta 3 carpetas activas
            </li>
          </ul>

          <button class="w-full py-4 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px]">
            Empieza Ahora
          </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Plan Plus (Destacado) -->
        <div class="group p-10 bg-[#1c1c21] border-2 border-blue rounded-[2.5rem] transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(59,130,246,0.15)] relative scale-105 z-20">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-blue text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest">
            Recomendado
          </div>
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-blue mb-2">Plus</h3>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 text-white">
              <span class="text-4xl font-black">$5.99</span>
              <span class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">/mes</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm mt-4">Incluye todas las características básicas más extras profesionales.</p>
          </div>
          
          <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 flex-grow">
            <li class="text-zinc-100 text-sm flex items-center gap-3 font-medium">
              <span class="text-blue">✓</span> Links ilimitados
            </li>
            <li class="text-zinc-100 text-sm flex items-center gap-3 font-medium">
              <span class="text-blue">✓</span> Código QR premium
            </li>
            <li class="text-zinc-100 text-sm flex items-center gap-3 font-medium">
              <span class="text-blue">✓</span> Carpetas ilimitadas
            </li>
          </ul>

          <button class="w-full py-4 bg-blue text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-blue/80 transition-all uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] shadow-lg shadow-blue/20">
            Elige Plus
          </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Plan Business -->
        <div class="group p-10 bg-[#18181b] border border-white/10 rounded-[2.5rem] hover:border-blue/50 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col shadow-2xl">
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-green-400 mb-2">Business</h3>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 text-white">
              <span class="text-4xl font-black">$9.99</span>
              <span class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">/mes</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm mt-4">Soporte prioritario y herramientas de marca avanzada.</p>
          </div>
          
          <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 flex-grow">
            <li class="text-zinc-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-400">✓</span> Todo lo del plan Plus
            </li>
            <li class="text-zinc-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-400">✓</span> Dominio personalizado
            </li>
            <li class="text-zinc-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-400">✓</span> Analíticas avanzadas
            </li>
          </ul>

          <button class="w-full py-4 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px]">
            Elige Business
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00f2ff 0%, #4ade80 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .custom-shadow {
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8));
  }

  .text-blue {
    color: #00f2ff;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .scale-105 {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
  }
</style>